shield.","year":-827},{"id":"recINQZEjpJJjEA8Q","ref":"2Chr.25.6","text":"He hired also an hundred thousand mighty men of valour out of Israel for an hundred talents of silver.","year":-827},{"id":"recpDoXdAH4TR2C0g","ref":"2Chr.25.7","text":"But there came a man of God to him, saying, O king, let not the army of Israel go with thee; for the LORD is not with Israel, to wit, with all the children of Ephraim.","year":-827},{"id":"recBw6OtTS1PidZ2z","ref":"2Chr.25.8","text":"But if thou wilt go, do it, be strong for the battle: God shall make thee fall before the enemy: for God hath power to help, and to cast down.","year":-827}]}
